            "title": "<strong>Riding Range Test | Ranger</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Max Range: 40 miles(pure electric) /55 miles(pedal assist)</p><p>*Note: Throttle Max Range tests are calculated using PAS 1 with a rider weight of 165 lbs on flat terrain. Throttle speed and range may vary if ridden in different conditions.</p>",
